  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is a pilot study. The purpose of this study is to determine whether adding 4 months of
      behavioral therapy to primary care physician medication treatment(relative to medication
      treatment alone) improves outcomes for persistently depressed primary care patients.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
